  "original_title": "\u0baf\u0bbe\u0bb4\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bc0\u0b9f\u0bc1 \u0baa\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bc1\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0baa\u0bc6\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0bb0\u0bcb\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Gasoline theft by house entry in Yali",
      "author": "Digital Desk 5",
      "body_lines": [
        "Jaffna. Two persons stole petrol from a motorcycle parked in a house near the district secretariat and fled.",
        "Two persons entered the said house around 2.30 am today, stole petrol from the motorcycle parked inside the house and escaped.",
        "Then this morning when the family got up and started the motorcycle, it was revealed that the petrol was stolen from the motorcycle while it was not running.",
        "After that, when checking the security surveillance camera installed in the house, it was revealed that two people trespassed inside the house and stole petrol on a motorcycle.",
        "In this case, it is noteworthy that the owner of the house has shared the video footage of him breaking into his house and stealing petrol on social media."
      ],
